snippet.title: TOKKI Gameplay
snippet.description:
Please help TOKKI in his search for his lost gems.

Gameplay for the new TOKKI game.

DEMO playable on Itch.io : 
https://zeno-g.itch.io/tokki
(Play in the browser. No download required)

Available soon on Steam am Google Play

Credits:
Programing: Zeno-Daniel Görbe
Visual Assets: Kenney Vleugels & Zeno-Daniel Görbe
Music: Juhani Junkala
SFX: Kenney Vleugels & Zeno-Daniel Görbe
